{
  "texts": [
    "For example, in Figure 1, Published plays the role of a collider on the path between Rigour and Novelty.",
    "That path is closed; we can open it by conditioning on Published.",
    "Finally, the third type of variable that we consider is a mediator.",
    "A mediator 𝑍 is always connected like 𝑋 → 𝑍 → 𝑌.",
    "Here, 𝑍 is affected by 𝑋 and in turn 𝑍 affects 𝑌, so that 𝑍 mediates the indirect causal effect of 𝑋 on 𝑌."
  ]
}